Headquarters Regions: Greater Boston Area, East Coast, New England
Full Description: The shortage of doctors, particularly in rural areas, makes getting the right specialist to the right place at the right time a challenge. Description: Seattle Urban Farm Company creators of beautifully productive landscapes.
Headquarters Regions: Greater Seattle Area, West Coast, Western US
Full Description: Seattle Urban Farm Company blends sustainable farming principles with ecological landscape design to create unique, productive outdoor spaces. Founded in 2007, co-owners Colin McCrate and Brad Halm wanted to apply their years of horticultural and agricultural expertise to help aspiring growers get projects off the ground or more accurately; in the ground: so they bought a truck, grabbed some shovels and got to work. Over the past eight years, we have helped guide hundreds of urban farmers through the design, construction and management of their own edible landscape. We work with our clients through the entire design/build process because we believe that cohesion and attention to detail are what make each project special and successful.  We pride ourselves on creating environmentally responsible and long-lasting garden elements. Sourcing quality materials and locally adapted plants ensures the long-term health and beauty of our landscapes.     Starting out as a two-man operation, SUFCo now has 15 urban farmers, each with unique skills and experience.  Our skilled staff and comprehensive approach allows us to create sustainable edible landscapes that are successful on a wide variety of sites and scales. We are committed to the immediate and ongoing success of all of our projects, focusing on intensive plantings and organic soil management to ensure high yields of crops season after season. Year after year we build new edible landscapes, manage dozens of backyard and rooftop urban farms and teach numerous classes and workshops across the region. With each new year, we find new opportunities and as public awareness of urban agriculture continues to grow, we hope to grow along with it and with you!   The Seattle Urban Farm Company is licensed, bonded, and insured in Washington State.
Industry Groups: Agriculture and Farming, Food and Beverage

Description: PicBackMan is a photo and video uploading website.
Headquarters Regions: San Francisco Bay Area, Silicon Valley, West Coast
Full Description: [PicBackMan](http://www.picbackman.com/) is a dead easy photo & video backup solution that allows users to automatically backup photos & videos from computers & social accounts to one or more online photo / storage services. PicBackMan also helps users to download their entire online collection on a local computer or migrate between their online accounts.  PicBackMan helps users connect online photo / storage accounts including Flickr, Picasa, SmugMug, SkyDrive, Box, Dropbox, Facebook, Google Drive, Photobucket and other so photos & videos can be backed up on one or more of these services. To auto backup, a user simply needs to associate the folders on her computer and choose where to back them to. Users can also auto backup photos & videos from social accounts like Instagram, Facebook and Foursquare. Once setup, PicBackMan works constantly to backup new photos & videos as they appear and continues to do so without any overhead for the user. PicBackMan marks all photos that it backups private so they are not available publicly ever. PicBackMan also uploads from parent and sub-folders so if an user associates the My Pictures folder, them PicBackMan uploads pictures from all the sub-folders under it as well, as separate albums based on the folder name.  PicBackMan was soft launched in May 2012 with full 1.0 launch in May 2013. PicBackMan has been downloaded in 200+ countries globally and has been used to backup millions of photos and videos. PicBackMan is based on San Jose, California.
Industry Groups: Content and Publishing, Hardware, Media and Entertainment
